<Body>  <Title>面包车起火 致十人伤亡</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2009年08月13日</ReportTime>
<Content>	
	
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1"><Time tid="t" type="relTime">昨天清晨6时许</Time>，一辆乘坐12人的超载<Object sid="s1,s2">面包车</Object><Denoter did="d1" type="movement">行驶</Denoter>至<Location lid="l1" type="destination">京承高速进京方向</Location>时</Event><Event eid="e2">突然<Denoter did="d2" type="action">起火</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e3"><Participant sid="s3">司机和副驾驶</Participant><Denoter did="d3" type="action">逃生</Denoter></Event>，而坐在车内的<Event eid="e4"><Participant oid="o4">10名木工</Participant>不同程度<Denoter did="d4" type="stateChange">烧伤</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e5">其中<Participant sid="s5">一人</Participant><Denoter did="d4" type="stateChange">死亡</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e6">据<Denoter did="d6" type="perception">了解</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e7"><Object sid="s7">面包车</Object>可能是<Denoter did="d7" type="action">自燃</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e8"><Participant oid="o8">司机</Participant>已被<Participant sid="s8">警方</Participant><Denoter did="d8" type="action">带走</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e9"><Denoter type="operation" did="d9">调查</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e10"><Time type="relTime" tid="t10">昨天清晨7时40分左右</Time>，<Participant sid="s10">记者</Participant><Denoter did="d10" type="movement">赶到</Denoter><Location lid="l10">事发现场――京承高速进京方向城铁望京西站</Location></Event>，<Event eid="e11"><Time tid="t11" type="relTime">此时</Time><Location lid="l11">现场</Location>已经<Denoter did="d11" type="operation">清理</Denoter>完毕</Event>，<Event eid="e12">但路边的<Object oid="o12">护栏</Object>已被<Denoter did="d12" type="action">撞</Denoter>得凹进去一大块</Event>，地上还有一摊黑灰。</Sentence><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e13">据一位城铁站内的<Participant sid="s13">工作人员</Participant><Denoter did="d13" type="statement">介绍</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e14"><Time type="relTime" tid="t14">清晨6时左右</Time>，<Object sid="s14">一辆面包车</Object>冒起熊熊<Denoter did="d14" type="emergency">大火</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e15"><Location lid="l15">离面包车不远处</Location><Participant sid="s15">几个人</Participant><Denoter did="d15" type="action">坐</Denoter>在地上</Event>，身上都有不同程度的伤，<Event eid="e16"><Participant sid="s16">有人</Participant>不停地<Denoter did="d16" type="action">喊</Denoter>救命</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e17">奥林匹克公园<Participant sid="s17">消防中队</Participant><Denoter did="d17" type="movement">赶到</Denoter><Location lid="l17" type="destination">现场</Location></Event>后，<Event eid="e18"><Time tid="t18" type="timeInterval">不到10分钟</Time>就将<Object oid="o18">火</Object><Denoter did="d18" type="operation">扑灭</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e19"><Participant oid="o19">999急救人员</Participant>同时对<Participant sid="s19">伤员</Participant>进行<Denoter did="d19" type="operation">救护</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>由于人手不够，<Event eid="e20">城铁站里的<Participant sid="s20,s21,s22">保安和周围一些好心人</Participant>也来帮忙把<Participant oid="o20,o21">伤者</Participant><Denoter did="d20" type="action">抬</Denoter>上<Means mid="m20" type="tool">担架</Means></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>“有几个人伤得不轻，<Event eid="e21"><Denoter did="d21" type="action">抬</Denoter>的时候</Event>都能<Event eid="e22"><Denoter did="d22" type="action">闻</Denoter>到很重的<Object oid="o22">烧焦味</Object></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e23"><Time tid="t23" type="relTime">大概7点10分左右</Time>，被烧的<Object oid="o23">面包车</Object>被<Denoter did="d23" type="action">拖走</Denoter>了</Event>。”</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e24"><Participant sid="s24">记者</Participant>随后<Denoter did="d24" type="movement">前往</Denoter><Location lid="l24" type="destination">北京军区总医院东院</Location></Event>，<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e25">烧伤整形科<Participant sid="s25">朱主任</Participant>介绍<Denoter did="d25" type="statement">说</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e26"><Denoter did="d26" type="movement">送到</Denoter><Location lid="l26">该院</Location>的<Participant oid="o26">有9名伤者</Participant></Event>，<Event eid="e27"><Participant oid="o27">4位重伤员</Participant>被<Denoter did="d27" type="movement">送往</Denoter><Location lid="l27" type="destination">重症监护室</Location>救治</Event>，烧伤面积均达到97%以上。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e28">截至<Denoter did="d28" type="operation">发稿</Denoter>时止</Event>，<Event eid="e29"><Participant sid="s29">4人</Participant>仍未<Denoter did="d29" type="action">脱离</Denoter>生命危险</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e30">而送到积水潭医院的<Participant sid="s30">另外一名伤者</Participant>已不幸<Denoter  did="d30" type="stateChange">死亡</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

